@@ -0,0 +1,21 @@
+# Neither Step-3 Comparator Outperforms The Direction-Plus-Tube Hybrid
+
+Status: `INFERRED`
+
+The Step-4 comparator audit sharpens the earlier Step-2 survivor story rather
+than overturning it. Under the fixed Eulerian parabolic package, neither
+standalone comparator beats the hybrid:
+
+- direction coherence keeps the route stretching-facing, but loses the only
+credible persistence bridge and falls back toward prior-art or hidden
+`nabla xi` control;
+- tube persistence keeps the Tao-sensitive intuition about coherent intense
+structures, but loses a stretching-facing mechanism and collapses toward static
+geometry or hidden relocalization.
+
+The live comparison point is therefore sharper than "the hybrid survived
+earlier screens." It is that the hybrid still looks necessary under the same
+localization package that defeats each half when audited on its own.
+
+Filed from:
+- `missions/beyond-de-giorgi/library-inbox/step-004-exploration-002-comparator-dynamic-audit.md`
